data.description: A great little home in the mountains. A gem of a home in the country, a quick get away from the city or a cabin to retreat to. Quick access to Helen, Georgia and the North Georgia Mountains. This 3 bedroom 2 bath home sits back in a mountain subdivision called Bakers Fiord. Turn off the main road of 384 also known as Duncan Bridge Road and onto Bakers Fiord Road and it will wind around past a small stream and will be on your left about a half of a mile down. Access the property through the open gate on your left. As you stand on the front porch of this property and look back up the driveway you will see the beautiful mountain views surrounding you. Home has a new HVAC system installed in 2022. Hardwood floors on the main level and carpet in the bedrooms. Home is in good shape but could use a little TLC.
